Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,睡着了
